  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">40C/5 ER10: Research and foresight, monitoring and reporting on SDG 4-Education 2030 have effectively generated evidence, recommendations and insight to advance progress towards SDG 4</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">UNESCO will generate evidence and pursue its normative role and monitoring function in view of increasing demand for equitable quality education provision, supporting the right to education, and ensuring that international commitments to education are met. Likewise, through research and foresight, UNESCO will provide knowledge, evidence and insight to help guide global policy and inform dialogue on the future of education, as well for country-based policy advice and technical assistance, and assist countries undertake operational activities and implement reforms that are in line with its agreed norms, standards and methodologies and which address SDG 4 goal and targets.</narrative>
  </description>
